Product name: Genuine Australian LEATHER Bow Tie - Repurposed Leathers with Character
Description:
Thank you for stopping by and looking at my genuine leather bow ties. I handcraft these bow ties using reclaimed Australian leathers which means they exude warmth and character. Once I have found the perfect leather I hand burnish the leather edges with beeswax which gives and elegant bevelled edge - it really sets our ties apart. I choose only to use heavy waxed cotton which provides a stunning contrast on your bowtie - but it's only on the reverse side, so for your enjoyment only!
Our bow ties are fastened using vintage styled leather fasteners and are fully adjustable for a great fit. The buckles I use are also repurposed. The tie is approx 10cm wide - however - if you would like a different width, please just let me know!
The leather bow tie is very popular not only for weddings, but for rodeo bull riders and looks amazing with a checked shirt! Dress it up or dress it down. Each bow tie is handmade and being made from a natural leather, it does feature all the eccentricities of natural leather. 
We are able to make ties in any colour of leather that you require, HOWEVER, as we make our bowties from reclaimed leathers, please check with me first if you require a shade other than a brown (as pictured) or black bowtie. We do have other leathers available, but they change constantly. If you have a leather that you would like to use, it's no trouble for you to send it to us and we can make your ties using that - but please be in touch first to ensure it's the right size etc etc.
Your bow tie is made to order and I will post it within 6 working days of receiving your order, if you choose and express order, it will be posted within 3 working days. 
Item Details

❤ Shipping
All shipping costs include tracking and/or signature on arrival. Insurance and International Express Shipping is not included but can be purchased for an additional charge.
For all Australian orders - please contact me directly and I will provide you with a quote for your postcode (postage in listings are set to furthest point from Sydney). You will have the option of regular, express or same day postage.
For all International orders - all orders are shipped standard with tracking, please contact me directly if you require another shipping option.

❤ Custom orders
Looking for something different? Need a package for your whole bridal party? Please feel free to contact me with your exact needs and I'll create something special just for you :)
Please note: For all custom order, please order at least 2-3 months in advance from your wedding day. This ensures extra time for perfecting your bouquet, shipping delays or anything unexpected popping up.
I am happy to help you in any way I possibly can!
